title: ONE MONTH FREE on all vacant homes and select units move in by 8/15
posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID # 71030', 'ONE MONTH FREE on all vacant homes and select units if you lease and move in by 8/15.', ' *min 12 month lease.', 'Come see all the new changes!', 'Newly renovated and expanded Pool Area with Outdoor Gas Grill and Fire Pit, New Health and Wellness Center, Dog Park Added, New Leasing Center with Coffee Bar, and Modern Painted Exterior with Modern Closed in Patios.', 'LUXURY APARTMENTS IN HOUSTON, TX', 'Experience the finest in amenities and service that we offer at our apartments for rent in Houston, TX.', 'Conveniently located with easy access to restaurants and shopping, join us to enjoy all that Houston has to offer.', 'EXPANDED SPARKLING SWIMMING POOL', 'NEW HEALTH AND WELLNESS CENTER', 'GAS GRILL', 'OUTDOOR FIRE PIT', 'Our stunning homes will provide the perfect backdrop for every lifestyle.', 'With a selection of one and two bedroom floor plans to choose from and an expansive community with unique features, our luxury apartments in Houston, TX easily accommodate every resident.', 'Within each home, residents will love the fully-equipped kitchens with all black appliances and expansive closets.', 'Throughout our community at our apartments for rent in Houston, TX, residents can take advantage of the beautiful swimming pool, fully-equipped fitness center, and large sundeck.', 'Aside from our amazing homes, residents will also enjoy our ideal location that brings them close to all that the city holds.', 'Our luxury apartments in North Houston are surrounded by a variety of dining and entertainment options and the heart of the city is a just a short drive away.', 'See why we offer the best apartments in Houston and explore all that our homes hold.']
